name: Milkshake Swap
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: MilkshakeSwap is a Binance Smart Chain-powered DEX and AMM that allows anyone to swap BEP-20 tokens efficiently and safely. The platform is comparable to Uniswap in that it provides a decentralized trading experience combined with liquidity pools. MilkshakeSwap can be the largest Dapp on the Binance Smart Chain and is seen by many as a project with endless potential. As such, the platform is very popular and currently has $5,497,727.35 in locked liquidity at this time.
